task.summary: Adds constructor for Customer as well as getter/setter methods and tests.
Adds constructors for all ride types.
Adds customer arraylists to constructors for all ride types.
Adds methods and tests for get customers ArrayList size.
Adds methods and tests for adding customers to rides and checking free space.
Updates methods and tests for adding customers to rides by checking free space.
Updates methods and tests for adding customers to rides by checking the age limit and their cash.
Updates methods and tests for adding customers to rides by adding them to a queue if the ride is full.
Adds a till property to ride and get/set tests and method.
Adds a PayForRide function, called within AddCustomerToRide, that decreases cash and increases till.
Adds interface IThrill and implements it in each concrete ride class; changes happiness to a double.
Adds tests and methods for thrill to increase customers happiness.
Adds minor tweaks moving away from setter methods for till and cash.
